1
00:01:20,799 --> 00:01:21,439
Xu Wenwen

2
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,920
You think by refusing to confess,

3
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,760
we won't be able to convict you?

4
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,040
Officers,

5
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,799
let me reiterate.

6
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,319
I'm flying abroad today

7
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:33,040
for an important business forum.

8
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:35,560
If you waste my time,

9
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,840
you officers will be held accountable.

10
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,640
Don't worry.

11
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,159
Whatever responsibility falls on us,

12
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:41,159
we will never shirk it.

13
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,640
But those people who died,

14
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,400
who should be held responsible?

15
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,920
Where's the evidence?

16
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,760
You claim Collusion with Su Zhuang.

17
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,319
I can explain.

18
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:56,719
We had a normal business partnership.

19
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,239
If there were any violations,

20
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,359
I'm willing to take responsibility.

21
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,799
Punish me as you see fit.

22
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,280
Sentence me as you see fit.

23
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,480
But murder?

24
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:09,120
That's too heavy a charge.

25
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:11,280
I can't bear it.

26
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,680
Stop making trouble.

27
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,240
I'm just a helpless woman.

28
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,639
With a gun to my head,

29
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:19,240
I'd say whatever they want me to say.

30
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,319
Ma Shijiang's mother, Qiu Huimin,

31
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,080
is your cousin, right?

32
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,479
That's correct.

33
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:28,080
And you arranged for Qiu Huimin to adopt Ma Shijiang?

34
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:30,360
Also correct.

35
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,960
So when Ma Shijiang committed his crimes,

36
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,919
you were the one who saved him.

37
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,840
Now that's a real injustice.

38
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:40,759
Since Ma Shijiang went to prison for

39
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:43,439
intentional assault, I cut all contact.

40
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,360
How could I have any dealings

41
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,759
with scum like him?

42
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,639
If you had no dealings with him,

43
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,840
why bribe Big Liu

44
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,879
to kill Ma Shijiang?

45
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,000
Officer,

46
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,560
where's the evidence?

47
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,840
This so-called Big Liu you mention,

48
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,400
I've never even met him.

49
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,120
Your personal assistant,

50
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,719
Sun Meng,

51
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,759
gave Big Liu 300,000 yuan.

52
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,080
You can't claim ignorance, can you?

53
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,280
That's right.

54
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,479
Sun Meng is my personal assistant,

55
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:19,000
and has been with me for years.

56
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,560
However,

57
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,120
whether she hid things from me

58
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,840
and did anything illegal,

59
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,080
I have no way of knowing.

60
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,960
If you don't believe me,

61
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:29,080
you can bring her here to confront me.

62
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,240
Rest assured of that.

63
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,039
I can guarantee you,

64
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,919
not a single criminal involved

65
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,199
will get away.

66
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,280
This Xu Wenwen is tough as nails.

67
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,840
With all the evidence we've laid out,

68
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,800
she still won't admit it.

69
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:54,039
That means our evidence isn't solid enough.

70
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,680
Xu Wenwen is a seasoned businesswoman.

71
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:58,159
To hide all these years without a slip up

72
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:01,199
means she's studied the law in depth,

73
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,800
and knows full well

74
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,439
that if our evidence chain is incomplete,

75
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,599
we can't truly convict her.

76
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,159
So what's our next move?

77
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,360
Break Xing Mingliang.

78
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,879
Find Sun Meng.

79
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,000
Any progress on that Wooden Cabin?

80
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:23,480
I was so focused on arresting Xu Wenwen,

81
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,279
I forgot to tell you.

82
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,399
I found the Wooden Cabin.

83
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,759
Inside Su Zhuang's car,

84
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,879
I found video on the dashcam memory card.

85
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,360
I traced its location from the footage.

86
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,600
You're unbelievable.

87
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,600
How could you forget something this important?

88
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,319
Where's the cabin?

89
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,399
Inside Dongjiao Lihu Wetland.

90
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:39,959
I checked into that place.

91
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,600
It was purchased privately.

92
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:43,120
The buyer was Su Zhuang's wife.

93
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,680
I was just about to head there.

94
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,800
Take me to the cabin.

95
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,399
Now.

96
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,040
Okay, sure.

97
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,319
Fang Ping.

98
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:16,639
You and Lin Xue, flank them from the side.

99
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:18,360
Don't fire unless necessary.

100
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:19,879
Jiang Han.

101
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,360
Don't move.

102
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,800
Boss, don't always shoulder it all alone.

103
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,920
It'll save you a lot of grief.

104
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,319
You rascal.

105
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,839
Where'd you pick up that smart mouth?

106
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:06,839
Hold still.

107
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,959
Where's Su Zhuang's key?

108
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,360
Something seems to be missing on the right.

109
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,240
Judging by the gap and position,

110
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,439
it should be another photo.

111
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,839
And about the same size as the left one.

112
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,639
If that's really the case,

113
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,439
then that photo

114
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,959
must be hiding a huge secret.

115
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,279
Sun Meng.

116
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,480
Don't think staying silent

117
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,439
will let you shoulder it all.

118
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,519
A few days ago,

119
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,839
a man tried to kill me.

120
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,519
Later, a body was pulled from the river.

121
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:49,959
Everyone said I was dead.

122
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,720
But I'm alive and well right now.

123
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,639
What are you getting at?

124
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:56,600
Nonsense.

125
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,160
My brother has already gone abroad.

126
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:05,560
That body had a tattoo on its arm,

127
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,199
identical to yours.

128
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:13,040
You killed my brother!

129
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,680
I'll kill you!

130
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,959
You'll pay for his life with yours!

131
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:16,839
Calm down.

132
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,759
Xu Wenwen killed your brother.

133
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,120
You take lives for her,

134
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:29,600
all to feed Xu Wenwen's greed.

135
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,320
Has she ever treated you like a person?

136
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:36,679
Don't try to turn me against my boss.

137
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,360
Our boss treats me and my brother

138
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:41,200
like her own children.

139
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,000
You're dead wrong.

140
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,840
She treats you as pawns,

141
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:47,679
pawns to move around at will.

142
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,320
Remember Wu Chengming, who Xu Wenwen used

143
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,559
to swindle that massive loan?

144
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:57,840
Don't know him.

145
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,399
He was arrested last night.

146
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:01,919
Today, he confessed everything.

147
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:26,559
Boss Wu

148
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,120
Sing us a song

149
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,840
Okay, okay

150
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,320
No, don't

151
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,879
No

152
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,200
We know

153
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:40,879
you're a victim too.

154
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:43,279
Xu Wenwen used you.

155
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,600
She set you up to be assaulted.

156
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,159
Then used the video as blackmail,

157
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,320
to swindle huge loans.

158
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,480
Liu Xiang

159
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,320
Shen Qing

160
00:09:58,759 --> 00:09:59,960
They were both pawns too.

161
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:07,080
You treated Xu Wenwen like a mother.

162
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,679
And how did she treat you?

163
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,679
What kind of mother

164
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,799
would push her child into a wolves' den

165
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,200
to suffer such humiliation?

166
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,559
And what kind of mother

167
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:21,360
would take her own child

168
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,600
and hand them over

169
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:24,440
to an irredeemable abyss of crime?

170
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:29,799
Say whatever you want.

171
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:32,120
I don't know anything.

172
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,480
Wu told the Economic Crimes Division

173
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,759
that Xu Wenwen introduced him to Su Zhuang

174
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,320
and had Shen Qing forge financial reports,

175
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,080
defrauding the bank of a 55 million loan.

176
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,840
This money,

177
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,080
initially,

178
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:56,159
Xu Wenwen, Su Zhuang, and Shen Qing

179
00:10:56,159 --> 00:10:57,679
split twelve million among them.

180
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:59,320
Later, Xu Wenwen chose to betray them.

181
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,519
She got Wu Chengming drunk and drugged him,

182
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,159
and set him up to rape Sun Meng.

183
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,480
Using that as leverage,

184
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,000
the kickback reached 20 million.

185
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,720
But Wu Chengming escaped.

186
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:10,279
Sun Tai caught him.

187
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,320
In the end, he paid 30 million

188
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,840
and was locked up by Xu Wenwen.

189
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:17,480
Based on Shen Qing's memory card,

190
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:19,919
the Economic Crimes Division reviewed

191
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:20,960
Shen Qing and Su Zhuang's recent loans.

192
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,639
They orchestrated multiple loan frauds

193
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,759
totaling over 300 million yuan.

194
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,799
We checked Sun Tai and Sun Meng's pasts,

195
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,879
and found both identities are fabricated.

196
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,000
The two siblings,

197
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,320
aside from Xu Wenwen and Su Zhuang,

198
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,200
have no connections with anyone else.

199
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,120
To put it plainly,

200
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,200
these two are like ghosts,

201
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,159
killers raised by Xu Wenwen.

202
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:42,039
Mm.

203
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,440
The case is getting clearer.

204
00:11:45,759 --> 00:11:46,799
No matter what obstacles arise,

205
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:48,399
we must break through quickly.

206
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:50,360
Jianjun

207
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,120
Old Chief

208
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,679
It's been so many years.

209
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:55,720
How's your health?

210
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:56,440
Good.

211
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,000
Aside from being a bit older than you,

212
00:11:58,159 --> 00:12:00,120
I'm in no way worse off than you.

213
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,080
Yes, yes, yes.

214
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,399
Here, please, have a seat.

215
00:12:03,159 --> 00:12:04,559
Let's cut to the chase.

216
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:05,840
I shouldn't have come here,

217
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,960
but it's urgent,

218
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,159
so I couldn't worry about that.

219
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:09,120
Take a look first

220
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,320
at this photo.

221
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,320
Who does it look like?

222
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,679
Isn't this Ma Shijiang?

223
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:24,360
What's the connection between these photos?

224
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,639
This man is Han Dajun, right?

225
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,639
Case 531 from 22 years ago.

226
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:33,919
The main suspect who jumped to his death.

227
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,039
That's right.

228
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,639
Look, who does this kid resemble?

229
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,519
This kid looks just like Ma Shijiang.

230
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,919
And the adult Ma Shijiang

231
00:12:45,279 --> 00:12:46,600
also looks like Han Dajun.

232
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,720
You get it now, don't you?

233
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,039
Ma Shijiang

234
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:52,320
is Han Dajun's biological son.

235
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,200
Are you certain?

236
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,559
Ma Shijiang's mother is Liu Mei.

237
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,960
We couldn't find her before

238
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,240
because she's in a psychiatric hospital.

239
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,320
Sometimes lucid, sometimes not.

240
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:05,559
The past events,

241
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,799
she's basically forgotten them all.

242
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,000
However,

243
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,840
she recognized at a glance

244
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,360
that the person in the photo

245
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,559
is Ma Shijiang.

246
00:13:13,759 --> 00:13:15,559
This is Liu Mei's hair.

247
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,799
Take it

248
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,919
and compare it with Ma Shijiang's DNA.

249
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,600
I understand.

250
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,480
I've found the breakthrough.

251
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,559
Lin Xue.

252
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:29,840
Take Sun Meng and Sun Tai's test results

253
00:13:30,279 --> 00:13:31,320
and run a comparison in the system.

254
00:13:31,919 --> 00:13:32,440
Yes, sir.

255
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,039
You must be hungry.

256
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:10,279
Taro Cake.

257
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:12,600
My favorite.

258
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,799
Go ahead and eat.

259
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,639
Let me tell you a story.

260
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:24,720
Use whatever tricks you've got.

261
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,480
Don't try that on me.

262
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,919
We met 22 years ago, one summer.

263
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,639
That day, for both of us,

264
00:14:35,159 --> 00:14:35,960
was a nightmare.

265
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,519
You...

266
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:44,840
Who the hell are you?

267
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,799
The little boy who held your hand

268
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,399
after you were hurt...

269
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,919
that was me.

270
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,639
Don't cry, don't cry.

271
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,799
You and your brother,

272
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,080
you were both chosen by Red Gloves, right?

273
00:15:12,759 --> 00:15:13,679
Once chosen,

274
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,320
you wouldn't be beaten anymore.

275
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,039
No more fear of being sold off.

276
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,320
I've searched for Red Gloves for years.

277
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:26,679
But he left no clues behind.

278
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,240
All I remember is...

279
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,159
his hands were very soft.

280
00:15:39,559 --> 00:15:41,080
Do you remember both of your real names?

281
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:05,320
My brother's name is Sun Tai.

282
00:16:05,759 --> 00:16:07,399
My name is Sun Meng.

283
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,120
Get out.

284
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,480
Get the hell out!

285
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,759
